						               													<description>After discovering the game and the 5 first cases as a detective or as the Chisel in &amp;quot;Enqu&amp;ecirc;tes &amp;agrave; Los Angeles&amp;quot; (the French version of Detective: City of Angels), you can know continue the experience with the 4 next cases.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;WARNING: You will need the core game to play with &amp;quot;Nouveaux Crimes&amp;quot; as the box will only contain the 4 new cases and the corresponding booklets.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Even if the different cases will be slightly harder one after the other, the game stays the same: a 3 to 9 players asymmetrical investigation game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The detectives will have to solve the case before their opponents. The Chisel will try to manage the story and how it's told, sometimes helping a detective in distress, sometimes slowing a lucky detective down, choosing the answers of the interrogated witnesses.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every game, dive deep into the nice film noir atmosphere of Los Angeles during the 40s.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
